Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:41.16,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}natsukashii bamen hodoite koboshita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:46.63,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}eranda ketsui wo shimetsukeru paradox
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:52.18,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}todokanai asu ni shizumeta
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:58.47,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}nigirishimeru kono te wo hirakeba
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:06.56,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}furete shimau tou ni nageta kibou
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:12.65,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}namida wo karashi mukau kono yami wo nuke
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:18.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}tsutsuganai mirai anata ga mitsumeteitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:24.12,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}yatto yatto tsukami kaketa hikari
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:28.09,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}daremo nanimo iwanakute ii
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:39.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\blur5}subete no kotae wa koko ni chanto aru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:35.49,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}As cores se espalham até onde o olhar alcança,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:41.16,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}uma cena nostálgica se desenrola e se espalham.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:46.63,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Um paradoxo que confunde nossas decisões,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.63,0:01:52.18,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}afundado em um amanhã inalcançável.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.84,0:01:58.47,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Se eu abrir essa mão que seguro com força,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.47,0:02:06.56,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}poderei alcançar a esperança que abandonei há muito tempo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:12.65,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Enxugue suas lágrimas e siga em frente para romper esta escuridão.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:18.79,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Mesmo quando você olha para um futuro sem esperança.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.79,0:02:24.12,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Eu finalmente, finalmente, comecei a entender a luz.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.12,0:02:28.09,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Não é preciso dizer nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.09,0:02:39.51,OP Trad,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur5}Porque todas as respostas estão bem aqui.
